{"tid":1964581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：美國停資助世衛　對國際抗疫合作產生消極影響","createTime":"2020-04-09T02:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T11:24:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":315,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bb9e56584f1f490a2f1949e520039a4ea6bd40","tid":1964581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普批評世衛非常「以中國為中心」，揚言考慮停止資助世衛。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示，在當前全球疫情形勢下，美方表示將暫停向世衛繳納會費，將對國際抗疫合作產生消極影響，希望各國同舟共濟，守望相助，共同為全球抗擊疫情作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，武漢肺炎疫情發生以來，世衛在總幹事譚德塞帶領下，在推動國際抗疫合作發揮重要作用，得到國際社會普遍認可和高度讚譽。剛結束的二十國集團領導人特別峰會發表聲明，強調要完全支持並承諾進一步增強世衛，在協調國際抗疫行動方面的職責。中方將一如既往堅定支援世衛，在全球抗疫合作中繼續發揮領導作用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1519590_1_20200408171059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1519590_1_20200408171059.jpg&h=ea75ec39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519590-20200408.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519590-20200408.htm&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ae6f4052\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519590-20200408.htm&h=672ce643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519590-20200408.htm</a>"},{"pid":"786cd370c15f1b24bb55788d9b38c95ecaca2782","tid":1964581,"uid":207462,"like":271,"dislike":0,"score":271,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"咁你咪科水囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e764857a875136787a08c5dd93b5d4d4bd1ad1","tid":1964581,"uid":337723,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔通好似你強國播毒對世界研究病毒有積極作用咩"},{"pid":"47ec725b47076da805e5481413d441049e1271f9","tid":1964581,"uid":54344,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-